        "Title": "ICA vs SherCorp Act 1 - Power Down",
        "Location": "LOCATION_WET_RAT",
        "PublicId": "130116806132",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/wet/scene_rat_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 47424c02-bb0f-4066-af5a-f1cdcdcd08b2).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. The Silica Police have asked us to find international Sher Corp presences after its founder, Dr. Sheridan, went into hiding over Project Blue&apos;s failure. We have located one in Chongqing that may be tampering with ICA operations. Eliminate three fake chefs identified by Silica Police as Sher Corp moles along with a certain Ms. Feng who has been stealing AI research data from both ICA and the Chinese government.\rMore information on Sher Corp will follow.\rGood hunting for now.",
